765
01:33:37,660 --> 01:33:42,688
Ferris, you're sick Don't push it
and make yourself worse

766
01:33:42,900 --> 01:33:47,132
- Maybe you're right, Dad
- I know I'm right, pal

767
01:33:47,340 --> 01:33:53,688
- How did you get to be so sweet?
- From years of practice

768
01:34:01,500 --> 01:34:04,458
Blanket

769
01:34:13,180 --> 01:34:15,296
Get well

770
01:34:19,780 --> 01:34:25,173
I'm going to get myself settled,
then I'll bring you a hot cup of soup

771
01:34:33,860 --> 01:34:40,174
I've said it before and I'll say
it again: Life moves pretty fast

772
01:34:40,380 --> 01:34:44,851
If you don't stop and look around
once in a while, you could miss it

773
01:34:54,460 --> 01:34:57,770
Four years I've been chasing this kid

774
01:34:57,980 --> 01:35:02,974
Four years he's been
making a fool of me

775
01:35:11,060 --> 01:35:16,259
Hey, Mr Rooney, what's going on?

776
01:35:17,420 --> 01:35:20,651
Did you get in a fight?

777
01:35:20,860 --> 01:35:24,091
Do you want a lift?

778
01:37:03,500 --> 01:37:08,449
I bet you never smelled
a real school bus before

779
01:37:20,780 --> 01:37:23,533
Gummi bear?

780
01:37:23,740 --> 01:37:28,018
They've been in my pocket
They're real warm and soft

781
01:38:12,540 --> 01:38:16,579
You're still here?

782
01:38:16,780 --> 01:38:19,817
